data.description: Makai Mortgage on Maui has confirmed that they are willing to finance a qualified buyer at 5.75% @1 point. And if the buyers were displaced by the Lahaina fires they can off 100% financing.   For all Veterans this condo is a VA assumable loan 2.75% inquire for details.  Remodeled in July 2023, this 2-bedroom / 2-bathroom condo is right across the street from Kihei Canoe Club, Dog Park, Basketball Court, and the OCEAN!! It takes one minute to get into the water from your private backyard gate. This condo has two fenced-in yards with an ocean view. New floors, trim, paint, ceiling fans, blinds, plugs, switches, and appliances have been installed. The master bathroom has mosaic rock with 3-D tile and a rain shower, while the other bathrooms have an "American Standard" Jacuzzi jet tub, along with Martha Stewart vanities and Pfister fixtures. The "Solid Oak" flooring with quartz countertops and bar are called "White Sparkle." There is a new stainless steel Whirlpool refrigerator with water purification and ice system added and an inset stainless steel kitchen sink with an "Insinkerator" disposal. There's also a new stainless steel Samsung dishwasher and a top air fryer stove from Samsung. LED lighting is installed throughout the condo, except for the bedrooms, which have new fanlights. The stacking laundry in the master bath is only one year old. The front yard has its own orchid tree, and the backyard has a private gated entrance that goes directly to the street, giving you beach access. The back yard offers ocean views and a built-in ground sprinkler system on a timer. The back cement lanai, which was just painted, has been extended for more room to entertain, and there's an outdoor shower for when you come in off the beach through your private entrance. The AC unit is a Carrier 24,000 BTU A/C split unit that was just serviced. One deeded parking stall is included. The building exterior was painted, and the roof was replaced in 2016. (Note: Pet lovers, you are allowed to have up to two animals.) Listor is owner
